Voilà pourquoi tu refuses de te transformer.

00:20:36.030 --> 00:20:36.640
Droite?

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:45.070
Pauvre petit garçon.

00:20:46.440 --> 00:20:47.370
Il y a des choses

00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:49.480
